**SECTION 2: SCORING ADJUSTMENTS**

Apply these adjustments to the base 10-factor score. All adjustments are
ADDITIVE (positives reduce score, negatives increase).

**2.1 REIT-Specific Additive Factors**

These factors ADD to the base score:

  ---------------------------- ------------ --------------------------------
  **Risk Factor**              **Points**   **Verification Source**

  Office (Class B/C) subsector **+12**      10-K property schedule; Costar
  baseline                                  data

  Office (Class A) subsector   **+8**       10-K property schedule; Costar
  baseline                                  data

  mREIT - Commercial baseline  **+8**       10-K loan schedule; CRE exposure
                                            %

  Life Science subsector       +6           10-K property type disclosure
  baseline                                  

  Healthcare - SNF subsector   +5           10-K operator coverage ratios
  baseline                                  

  mREIT - Agency baseline (ORC +4           10-K portfolio composition
  case)                                     

  Mall (Class A) subsector     +4           10-K tenant roster; anchor mix
  baseline                                  

  AFFO payout ratio \>110%     **+8**       Quarterly 8-K; calculate
                                            DIV/AFFO

  AFFO payout ratio 95-110%    **+6**       Quarterly 8-K; calculate
                                            DIV/AFFO

  AFFO payout ratio 90-95%     +3           Quarterly 8-K; calculate
                                            DIV/AFFO

  External management          +3           DEF 14A; management agreement
  structure                                 

  External mgmt + related      **+5**       DEF 14A Item 13; 10-K related
  party txns                                party

  Dividend cut \<12 months     **+6**       8-K dividend announcements

  Dividend cut 12-24 months    **+5**       Historical dividend record

  Multiple dividend cuts (3+)  +4           Full dividend history review

  mREIT book value decline     **+8**       10-K/10-Q BV per share
  \>40% YoY                                 

  mREIT book value decline     **+5**       10-K/10-Q BV per share
  20-40% YoY                                

  mREIT book value decline     +3           10-K/10-Q BV per share
  10-20% YoY                                

  Debt maturing \<24mo \>40%   **+6**       10-K debt maturity schedule

  Debt maturing \<24mo 30-40%  +4           10-K debt maturity schedule

  Debt/EBITDA \>8x (equity     **+5**       10-K MD&A; calculate ratio
  REIT)                                     

  Short interest \>15%         **+5**       Fintel, MarketBeat

  Short interest 8-15%         +3           Fintel, MarketBeat

  AFFO excludes recurring      +4           10-K AFFO reconciliation vs
  CapEx unlike peers                        peers

  AFFO methodology changed     +3           Compare sequential 10-K AFFO
  \<12 months                               tables
